&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;it’s important to place it as a child of TrackingSpace so that hands will move properly with the player, head, and hand movements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add a ground plane to prevent the player from falling and use a cube for reference&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;add a Plane 3D Object to act as the ground so you don’t fall infinitely &lt;br&gt; 
