&lt;h2&gt;Final thoughts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have now added basic Oculus Touch controller support to our scene including navigation and tracked hands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stay tuned, next time we will add the ability to grab an object with our hands.&lt;/p&gt;
