&lt;h2&gt;Enable VR support&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open the Edit menu &gt; Project Settings &gt; Player&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Under the Inspector &gt; expand XR Settings &gt; check Virtual Reality Supported&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;make sure Oculus is included under Virtual Reality SDKs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;if not, click the &lt;em&gt;+&lt;/em&gt; and add Oculus&lt;/li&gt;
