&lt;p&gt;We don’t have anything to look at, so first let’s add a cube to the scene&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;from Hierarchy, click Create &gt; 3D Object &gt; Cube&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Position the cube in front of the Main Camera&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;I set the cube’s Position to 0,0,-7 via the Inspector&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now, make sure your Rift and sensors are connected and set up and open the Oculus application.&lt;/p&gt;
